      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LORETTA KEEPING (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (30.18) at this track behind King Canelo in a Maiden. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Sure to be about the mark. QUEEN CARAMEL (3) is a Michael Hodges-trained newcomer by Feral Franky out of Queen Bolt with no trial form to work with. Profiles well but prefer to see a move in betting. CORLESS DEVIOUS (2) makes his first outing and has drawn to advantage. Can kick off with a good run. CHAOTIC BOY (8) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
